"```sql\nSELECT users.DisplayName, users.Reputation\nFROM posts\nJOIN users ON posts.OwnerUserId = users.Id\nWHERE posts.Id = 1;\n```\n\nThis SQL query retrieves the display name and reputation of the user who created the post with ID 1. It uses a JOIN operation to connect the `posts` table with the `users` table based on the foreign key relationship between `posts.OwnerUserId` and `users.Id`."